## 📝 Logging

- **Format**: Structured JSON logs
- **Levels**: `debug`, `info`, `warn`, `error`
- **Sensitive Data**: Never log PII, tokens, or passwords
- **Retention**: 30 days for development, 90 days for production

---

## 🔔 Alerting

| Condition | Severity | Action |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| Error rate > 5% | Critical | Notify on-call |
| API latency > 2s | Warning | Investigate during business hours |
| Disk space < 10% | Warning | Scale up storage |

